{"tid":1505281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［代po］關於狗鐵不合作運動一事","createTime":"2019-08-25T13:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T17:20:12.000Z","uid":132129,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15ffe6592b6d732087352ca9d19d99028de0b815","tid":1505281,"uid":132129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:29:02.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，<br />\n我是個狗鐵車站助理。<br />\n<br />\n8月5號朝早罷工雖然成功令觀塘線停咗，但都只係停得個幾個鐘，對狗鐵嚟講影響根本唔大！你有你罷，佢有佢賺。<br />\n<br />\n近兩個月嚟有唔少狗鐵不合作運動，只要每次有消息話會有狗鐵不合作活動嘅時候，狗鐵都會預先做勁多準備。例如會提早一日吹雞搵多啲人返嚟幫手，或者叫同事幫手OT，咁就會令到個站有勁多狗鐵人係到幫手維持秩序。<br />\n<br />\n朝早手足好努力咁阻門成功阻到車開，冇錯，月台嘅車停曬，但狗鐵仲有其他應變方法，佢地會準備免費巴士，而免費巴係爆鍋後八個字就standby出發，搞到啲藍絲仲可以上免費巴返工。過咗繁忙時間，因為狗鐵職員多，勁快搞返掂，開返條線，繼續食你水。<br />\n<br />\n而狗鐵通常都係0700-1000同1600-2200呢啲繁忙時間都會有好多職員係月台，而好少會有職員企係出口位置，啲免費巴通常係係個站唔知咩咩咩出口對出，與其搞月台，不如搞搞個出口，入又入唔到，出又出唔到，連錢都唔撚洗比佢賺。同埋狗鐵職員需多，清潔工一個站都唔多過十個，一人一隻雞蛋放一放係出口，個陣味都夠做。"},{"pid":"a64d228a1509558a955dffe34348a72ed22749d7","tid":1505281,"uid":71085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BjPzvju.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBjPzvju.png&h=4a040288&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/apwFqSP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FapwFqSP.png&h=ea587519&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3a690b22925a2a303bdebe3c4fee1f9b41dd815","tid":1505281,"uid":164043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:35:58.000Z","msg":"千萬不要"},{"pid":"2e6dc1acba96bf9fe6d099bec7ec9949f7db7cbc","tid":1505281,"uid":132129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:18:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a2f8c8960afab26aea6e4c646405080c4ee96fd","tid":1505281,"uid":132129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:18:59.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"fb13c3d1f539a9184771cdef848841871c9e2790","tid":1505281,"uid":132129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:19:09.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"1e17c57bd595f01fd1d864094dd71aeabfa179e7","tid":1505281,"uid":132129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:19:19.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"45458eb48a3082a05e1f637e66817dcfbb7bb75a","tid":1505281,"uid":132129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:19:29.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"7dbad676752df172139ba75024f3bbcd1b5c15a2","tid":1505281,"uid":132129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:19:47.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"e8627e789fb07e9080398c9220fd461fceb8eaa6","tid":1505281,"uid":132129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:20:00.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"86a757a5d5e7fd7930edc0a69c6a2c5c48aed538","tid":1505281,"uid":132129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:20:12.000Z","msg":"4"}]}